trans-unit.source: Performs a cryptographic transformation of data using the Rijndael algorithm.
trans-unit.target: Utför en kryptografisk transformering av data med hjälp av algoritmen Rijndael.

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: Den här klassen kan inte ärvas.

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > Using this class is not recommended.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE]> Du bör inte använda den här klassen.

trans-unit.source: A better practice is to use <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.RijndaelManaged> with a <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.CryptoStream> object.
trans-unit.target: En bättre metod är att använda <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.RijndaelManaged>med en <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.CryptoStream>objektet.</xref:System.Security.Cryptography.CryptoStream> </xref:System.Security.Cryptography.RijndaelManaged>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.CryptoStream> object handles the padding issues that can occur when using RijndaelManagedTransform directly.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.CryptoStream>objektet hanterar utfyllnad problem som kan uppstå när du använder RijndaelManagedTransform direkt.</xref:System.Security.Cryptography.CryptoStream>

trans-unit.source: For an example, see the <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.RijndaelManaged> class.
trans-unit.target: Ett exempel finns <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.RijndaelManaged>klass.</xref:System.Security.Cryptography.RijndaelManaged>

trans-unit.source: Both the <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.RijndaelManaged.CreateEncryptor%2A> and <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.RijndaelManaged.CreateDecryptor%2A> methods return an instance of the RijndaelManagedTransform class that is initialized with the key information of the current <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.RijndaelManaged> object.
trans-unit.target: Både den <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.RijndaelManaged.CreateEncryptor%2A>och <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.RijndaelManaged.CreateDecryptor%2A>metoder returnerar en instans av klassen RijndaelManagedTransform har initierats med viktig information för aktuellt <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.RijndaelManaged>objektet.</xref:System.Security.Cryptography.RijndaelManaged> </xref:System.Security.Cryptography.RijndaelManaged.CreateDecryptor%2A> </xref:System.Security.Cryptography.RijndaelManaged.CreateEncryptor%2A>

trans-unit.source: To encrypt or decrypt data using the Rijndael algorithm, pass the RijndaelManagedTransform object returned by these methods to a <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.CryptoStream> object.
trans-unit.target: Om du vill kryptera eller dekryptera data med hjälp av algoritmen Rijndael, skicka RijndaelManagedTransform-objektet som returnerades av dessa metoder till en <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.CryptoStream>objektet.</xref:System.Security.Cryptography.CryptoStream>

trans-unit.source: Releases all resources used by the <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.RijndaelManagedTransform"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Frigör alla resurser som används av den <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.RijndaelManagedTransform"> </xref> klass.

trans-unit.source: This method is a simple call to <xref:System.IDisposable.Dispose%2A?displayProperty=fullName> class.
trans-unit.target: Den här metoden är ett enkelt anrop till <xref:System.IDisposable.Dispose%2A?displayProperty=fullName>klass.</xref:System.IDisposable.Dispose%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: Calling `Dispose` allows the resources used by the <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.RijndaelManagedTransform> to be reallocated for other purposes.
trans-unit.target: Anropar `Dispose` tillåter resurserna som används av den <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.RijndaelManagedTransform>att fördelas för andra ändamål.</xref:System.Security.Cryptography.RijndaelManagedTransform>

trans-unit.source: For more information about `Dispose`, see [Cleaning Up Unmanaged Resources](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: Mer information om `Dispose`, se [Rensa ohanterade resurser](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: Releases all resources used by the current instance of the <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.RijndaelManagedTransform"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Frigör alla resurser som används av den aktuella instansen av den <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.RijndaelManagedTransform"> </xref> klass.

trans-unit.source: Call `Dispose` when you are finished using the <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.RijndaelManagedTransform>.
trans-unit.target: Anropa `Dispose` när du är klar med hjälp av <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.RijndaelManagedTransform>.</xref:System.Security.Cryptography.RijndaelManagedTransform>

trans-unit.source: The `Dispose` method leaves the <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.RijndaelManagedTransform> in an unusable state.
trans-unit.target: Den `Dispose` metoden lämnar kvar det <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.RijndaelManagedTransform>oanvändbar.</xref:System.Security.Cryptography.RijndaelManagedTransform>

trans-unit.source: After calling `Dispose`, you must release all references to the <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.RijndaelManagedTransform> so the garbage collector can reclaim the memory that the <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.RijndaelManagedTransform> was occupying.
trans-unit.target: Efter att `Dispose`, måste du släppa alla referenser till den <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.RijndaelManagedTransform>så skräpinsamlingen kan frigöra minne som den <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.RijndaelManagedTransform>var upptar.</xref:System.Security.Cryptography.RijndaelManagedTransform> </xref:System.Security.Cryptography.RijndaelManagedTransform>

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [Cleaning Up Unmanaged Resources](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) and [Implementing a Dispose Method](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: Mer information finns i [Rensa ohanterade resurser](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) och [implementera en metod för ta bort](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > Always call `Dispose` before you release your last reference to the <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.RijndaelManagedTransform>.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Alltid anropet `Dispose` innan du släpper senaste referens till <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.RijndaelManagedTransform>.</xref:System.Security.Cryptography.RijndaelManagedTransform>

trans-unit.source: Otherwise, the resources it is using will not be freed until the garbage collector calls the <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.RijndaelManagedTransform> object's `Finalize` method.
trans-unit.target: De resurser som den använder frigörs annars inte förrän skräpinsamlingen anrop av <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.RijndaelManagedTransform>objektets `Finalize` metod.</xref:System.Security.Cryptography.RijndaelManagedTransform>

trans-unit.source: Resets the internal state of <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.RijndaelManagedTransform"></xref> so it can be used again to do a different encryption or decryption.
trans-unit.target: Återställer det interna tillståndet för <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.RijndaelManagedTransform"> </xref> så att den kan användas igen att göra en annan kryptering eller dekryptering.

trans-unit.source: The Reset method is called automatically when you call <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.RijndaelManagedTransform.TransformFinalBlock%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Reset-metoden anropas automatiskt när du anropar <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.RijndaelManagedTransform.TransformFinalBlock%2A>.</xref:System.Security.Cryptography.RijndaelManagedTransform.TransformFinalBlock%2A>

trans-unit.source: The Reset method is not called when, for example, the encrypted input data is garbage and cannot be decrypted.
trans-unit.target: Reset-metoden anropas inte när exempelvis den krypterade indata är skräp och kan inte dekrypteras.

trans-unit.source: In this case, an exception is thrown and Reset is not called.
trans-unit.target: I det här fallet ett undantag genereras och Reset anropas inte.

trans-unit.source: You can choose to manually call the Reset method in this case.
trans-unit.target: Du kan välja att manuellt anropa metoden återställning i det här fallet.
